  "title": "Temporary Staff Admin - Creative, Media & Design - Up to $2,300",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><p>- Liaise with internal and external partners, and support logistics to successfully implement internal events and activities helmed by dept (e.g., company Townhalls, workplan retreats, staff engagements)</p><p>- Support design and development work for videos and internal communication pieces that the department requires e.g., basic video editing, Electronic Direct Mail (EDM) design, collaterals such as slides; and disseminate them to relevant parties</p><p>- Support the various administrative and operational needs of the department<br /></p><p><strong>Specific Requirements</strong></p><p>- Preferably relevant experience in video editing and design work</p><p>- Proficient in Microsoft Office applications (Word, Excel)</p><p>- Good analytical and communication skills</p><p>- Organised and meticulous</p><p>- Ability to work collaboratively within CSC and with external partners</p><p>- Demonstrate integrity and drive for excellence in work</p>",
